            <title>[THRIFT-1370] Debian packaging should Build-Depend on libglib2.0-dev</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1370</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Debian packaging builds the c_glib interface library, but does not name libglib2.0-dev as a Build-Dependency. While this usually won&apos;t affect manual builds, this is a problem for automated build environments which will not have libglib2.0-dev installed unless explicitly requested by Build-Depends.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
