&lt;p&gt;The Debian packaging builds the c_glib interface library, but does not name libglib2.0-dev as a Build-Dependency. While this usually won&apos;t affect manual builds, this is a problem for automated build environments which will not have libglib2.0-dev installed unless explicitly requested by Build-Depends.&lt;/p&gt;

